Titolo: John Wick Hex

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: John Wick Hex is a neo-noir action strategy video game based on the John Wick franchise. It was released on 8 October 2019 for Microsoft Windows and macOS. The PlayStation 4 port of the game released on 5 May 2020. The Xbox One and Nintendo Switch ports of the game were released on 4 December 2020. The game was developed by British studio Bithell Games and is distributed by Good Shepherd Entertainment. The game serves as a narrative prequel to the film series.

Genere: Action 

Valutazione: 73
